title: Cartoon - Alvin and the Chipmunks - Part 4
description:
Here are all the remaining episodes that I have for Alvin and the Chipmunks. Included episodes are 53,54,58,59,60,61,62,63,74,93,101 as well as the Christmas Special and Rockin through the Decades hosted by Will Smith. Enjoy and please seed.

NOTE: If you downloaded Part 2 of my collection you might notice that there is an episode 53 included. Acording to http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_Alvin_and_the_Chipmunks_episodes#Season_1_.281983.29 there are two episode 53&#039;s, I&#039;m not sure why.
